<br>
Pets, as with all other magic attacks, do less damge in PvP encounters.  This has been the case since shortly after Vallon and Tallon Zek went live, as naked mages were running around killing everyone, especially melee.  <br>
<br>
Recently, one thing has chanegd however, as velious increased the resists of people to some amazing levels.  The malo/tash/scent lines of spells now all decrease resists by an additional 50 percent when used against a PC.  This was done to compensate for the less damage done by the spell, so that the spell lands more often.  <br>
<br>
